source.name: Eastern U.S. Imagery
source.description: This product includes 10 km, remapped, GOES-East images in visible and ir bands (shortwave ir, water vapor, and longwave ir) and loops in Flash and Java.  The IR images are available in the following enhancements: AVN, Dvorak, JSL, RGB, Funktop, and Rainbow. This product is generated every 30 minutes.
